column5: First time posting so go easy on me. Looking for some recommendations for a lodge in September that offer 3 or 4 day plans for 4 people. Nothing fancy just a cabin and a couple boats. Target fish would be walleye and pike. Thanks
O'Sullivan's Rainbow, near Nakina. Also a chance for lake trout. Bill
Whitewing Resort on Lac Seul. Great owners and very nice facilities.www.whitewingresort.com
Birch Dale Lodge on Eagle Lake. www.birchdalelodge.com Give Marcel a call at 807-227-5262 and he should be able to help you out.
Evergreen Lodge out of Ear Falls. Coated on Lac Seul Great cabins and equipment.
